    - on_submit(): Submit the current guess, evaluate, and update board; handle win/lose.
    - on_clear(): Clear current guess.
    - on_undo(): Remove last color from current guess.
    - add_history_row(guess, exact, partial, index): Add a new row showing guess and pegs.
    - draw_pegs(canvas, exact, partial): Draw feedback pegs (black=exact, white=partial).
